        see:every example computed its own Voronoiology — six datasets crushed in parallel each to its own reading world beside its data
        see:a population folds where lone kinds cannot — twelve boulders gang behind one pane while eight single kinds stay bare below the minimum
        see:the groves keep their own panes — three nested containers fold outermost into three cells and the crush never descends inside
        see:the model discovers order from the data — the gradient example reads depth as a numeric axis and pins its ten strata from one end anchor to the other
